<!-- 产品介绍 -->
<section id="products" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<h2 class="inline-block text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">产品介绍</h2>
<div class="w-20 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto"></div>
<p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">我们的动力电池梯次利用解决方案集成多项创新技术，提供全面的电池回收与再利用服务</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-16">
<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
<div class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 rounded-full mb-4">
<i class="ri-filter-2-line text-primary text-xl"></i>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">电池分类功能</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600">可回收多种电池，采用实验估计法和高性能芯片、算法测算剩余容量，实现高效分类，二次包装外壳安全可靠。</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
<div class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 rounded-full mb-4">
<i class="ri-refresh-line text-primary text-xl"></i>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">电芯修复功能</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600">利用电化学方法，通过小电流充放电循环提升电池容量，自主设计电源满足修复需求，显著延长电池使用寿命。</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
<div class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 rounded-full mb-4">
<i class="ri-database-2-line text-primary text-xl"></i>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">电池管理功能</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600">自主设计的管理系统分上、下位机，具备数据采集等功能，用 CAN 通讯保障汽车通信，实现精准监控管理。</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition">
<div class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 rounded-full mb-4">
<i class="ri-alarm-warning-line text-primary text-xl"></i>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">环境监测与报警</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600">采用高主频芯片、防爆模块采集环境信息，通过 BDS 定位实现精准坐标报警，分级报警保障安全运行。</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
